&lt;div id="introduction" class="section level2"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over Christmas 2017, my wife, &lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/jillturner117/"&gt;Jill&lt;/a&gt;, resolved that our family (to include babysitters) would read our children over 1000 new books in 2018. More specifically, 29 December 2017 - 28 December 2018.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A goal like this takes dedication, love, and of course, a Data Science-y approach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Special thanks to Ally, Zia, and &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bookbuddy-pro-library-manager/id395149950?mt=8"&gt;Bookbuddy&lt;/a&gt; for help in accomplishing this goal!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, special thanks to &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/drob"&gt;drob&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/juliasilge"&gt;juliasilge&lt;/a&gt; who privde the &lt;code&gt;tidytext&lt;/code&gt; package and the entire R open-source community I rely on to do this analysis.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>